text:
The tables and floor were kept clean & wiped after each customer left. 👍🏻🤩

It is cooling to dine here due to multiple fans installed.

There are a few stalls here selling cuisines from Vietnamese, Malay, Indian, Chinese soup, drink stall and Mookata here.
The kopi so expensive 🫠. The drink shop dude put my kopi in a takeaway cup even when I was having here.
The water chestnut drink tasted spoiled to me and my partner. I informed the drink seller who tried it and just said it tasted fine. Do be careful of it. Not sure how long they kept it in the fridge.
